data.description: Don't miss the opportunity to own this charming Ranch. Investment opportunity for rehab/rental or make it your own with some TLC. Home has a ton of potential with some updates! Originally a 3 Bedroom and could easily be converted back. NEW Roof June of 2022, Newer PVC Plumbing Stack, Newer Water Heater and HVAC. New Carpeting in both Bedrooms Sept. 2023.  Hardwood floors in Living Room and under carpeting in both bedrooms! Updated Electric Panel and Remodeled Bathroom! Partially finished basement with more living space! 1-car carport! Deck off Kitchen! Fenced level yard! This home offers a combination of practical features with the potential for customization! And with a convenient location close to shopping, dining, and entertainment, you'll have everything you need right at your fingertips. Offered in its current AS IS condition. Schedule a Showing TODAY!
